{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"17941-bazaar-jaie","title":"બજાર જઈએ","description":"આપણે શું કર્યું, કયાં ગયા હતા, વગેરે કહેવાની બાળકોને ખૂબ જ મજા આવે છે. આ બાળક પણ ઉત્સુક છે – તે બજારમાં ગયો એ વિશે કહેવા માટે.","language":"Gujarati","langCode":"gu","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Veena Bhachech"],"illustrators":["Rijuta Ghate","Santosh Pujari"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Pratham Books","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/17941-bazaar-jaie"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/722697/size3/70f63c77cc485a7dc8880d6fe0eb2958.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/722697/size6/70f63c77cc485a7dc8880d6fe0eb2958.jpg"},"audio":{"src":"https://storage.googleapis.com/story-weaver-e2e-production/stories/17941/audios/story/17941-bazaar-jaie.mp3","cues":null},"pages":[{"n":1,"img":null,"text":"“ઓ મા! કેટલી ગરદી છે!”\n“આને બજાર કહેવાય.\nઅહીંથી જાતભાતની\nવસ્તુઓ ખરીદી શકાય.”","words":[[1,"“ઓ"],[2,"મા!"],[3,"કેટલી"],[4,"ગરદી"],[5,"છે!”"],[6,"“આને"],[7,"બજાર"],[8,"કહેવાય."],[9,"અહીંથી"],[10,"જાતભાતની"],[11,"વસ્તુઓ"],[12,"ખરીદી"],[13,"શકાય.”"]]},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/42193/size6/a90c7d94fac6a3b690460dc258543b9b.jpg","text":"3/20","words":null},{"n":3,"img":null,"text":"“આ શું છે?”\n“અનાજ-કરિયાણાની દુકાન.\nઆપણે પાંચ કિલો\nચોખા ખરીદીશું.”","words":[[14,"“આ"],[15,"શું"],[16,"છે?”"],[17,"“અનાજ-કરિયાણાની"],[18,"દુકાન."],[19,"આપણે"],[20,"પાંચ"],[21,"કિલો"],[22,"ચોખા"],[23,"ખરીદીશું.”"]]},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/42194/size6/2ea44d9f97f190b8ad6a8eaf5f89ec13.jpg","text":"5/20","words":null},{"n":5,"img":null,"text":"“આ શાકની દુકાનને, મા?\nઆપણે પાંચ કિલો કોથમીર લઈશું?”\n“ના, ફક્ત એક ઝૂડી.”","words":[[24,"“આ"],[25,"શાકની"],[26,"દુકાનને,"],[27,"મા?"],[28,"આપણે"],[29,"પાંચ"],[30,"કિલો"],[31,"કોથમીર"],[32,"લઈશું?”"],[33,"“ના,"],[34,"ફક્ત"],[35,"એક"],[36,"ઝૂડી.”"]]},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/42195/size6/569a7308f84841e53729b1d4aae90dbc.jpg","text":"7/20","words":null},{"n":7,"img":null,"text":"“મા, અહીં તો કેવી ચીકણી ગંધ છે!”\n“હા, તેલની દુકાન છે.\nઆપણે બે લિટર તેલ લઈશું.”","words":[[37,"“મા,"],[38,"અહીં"],[39,"તો"],[40,"કેવી"],[41,"ચીકણી"],[42,"ગંધ"],[43,"છે!”"],[44,"“હા,"],[45,"તેલની"],[46,"દુકાન"],[47,"છે."],[48,"આપણે"],[49,"બે"],[50,"લિટર"],[51,"તેલ"],[52,"લઈશું.”"]]},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/42196/size6/3edaf62fb040bc80f21623ba96f7751d.jpg","text":"9/20","words":null},{"n":9,"img":null,"text":"“આ તો જોતાં જ ખબર પડી ગઈ –\nમચ્છી બજાર.”\nમા અહીંથી કશું લેતી નથી.","words":[[53,"“આ"],[54,"તો"],[55,"જોતાં"],[56,"જ"],[57,"ખબર"],[58,"પડી"],[59,"ગઈ"],[60,"–"],[61,"મચ્છી"],[62,"બજાર.”"],[63,"મા"],[64,"અહીંથી"],[65,"કશું"],[66,"લેતી"],[67,"નથી."]]},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/42197/size6/d0640373a9c0fa9fcb0eabadafff0000.jpg","text":"11/20","words":null},{"n":11,"img":null,"text":"“મા, જો, દૂધની દુકાન!”\n“આજે આપણે ડેરીએથી\nકશું જ ખરીદવું નથી.”","words":[[68,"“મા,"],[69,"જો,"],[70,"દૂધની"],[71,"દુકાન!”"],[72,"“આજે"],[73,"આપણે"],[74,"ડેરીએથી"],[75,"કશું"],[76,"જ"],[77,"ખરીદવું"],[78,"નથી.”"]]},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/42198/size6/064710a9435dbb0c6257bf1acb93a2ba.jpg","text":"13/20","words":null},{"n":13,"img":null,"text":"“મા, જો, દૂધની દુકાન!”\n“આજે આપણે ડેરીએથી\nકશું જ ખરીદવું નથી.”","words":[[79,"“મા,"],[80,"જો,"],[81,"દૂધની"],[82,"દુકાન!”"],[83,"“આજે"],[84,"આપણે"],[85,"ડેરીએથી"],[86,"કશું"],[87,"જ"],[88,"ખરીદવું"],[89,"નથી.”"]]},{"n":14,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/42199/size6/01f52b1aff52cba27dab23a3833db652.jpg","text":"15/20","words":null},{"n":15,"img":null,"text":"“મા, આ દરજીની દુકાન છે?”\n“ના, કાપડીની.\nઆપણે દાદી માટે પાંચ\nમીટરની સાડી લઈશું.”","words":[[90,"“મા,"],[91,"આ"],[92,"દરજીની"],[93,"દુકાન"],[94,"છે?”"],[95,"“ના,"],[96,"કાપડીની."],[97,"આપણે"],[98,"દાદી"],[99,"માટે"],[100,"પાંચ"],[101,"મીટરની"],[102,"સાડી"],[103,"લઈશું.”"]]},{"n":16,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/42200/size6/b5496abdb80a58857b015f2fecad0e03.jpg","text":"17/20","words":null},{"n":17,"img":null,"text":"“મા, આ દરજીની દુકાન છે?”\n“ના, કાપડીની.\nઆપણે દાદી માટે પાંચ\nમીટરની સાડી લઈશું.”","words":[[104,"“મા,"],[105,"આ"],[106,"દરજીની"],[107,"દુકાન"],[108,"છે?”"],[109,"“ના,"],[110,"કાપડીની."],[111,"આપણે"],[112,"દાદી"],[113,"માટે"],[114,"પાંચ"],[115,"મીટરની"],[116,"સાડી"],[117,"લઈશું.”"]]},{"n":18,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/42201/size6/b1db025a46e21fc25c620eeb4f41c88f.jpg","text":"19/20","words":null},{"n":19,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/42202/size6/432083471bec8126a75a0da8b6e8e3f5.jpg","text":"20/20","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":19,"words":127}}